        <section name="What is Hippo Site Toolkit 2?">
        
            <p>
                Hippo Site Toolkit 2 is an open source toolkit for Java web developers,
                to build websites based on <a href="http://docs.onehippo.org/hippo-ecm">Hippo CMS 7</a>.
                Assemble your website by configuring templates, site map, navigation and URL space through 
                a straightforward user interface, that integrates with Hippo CMS. Create a JSP based view 
                layer using the provided tag library and expression language. 
            </p>
            
